HEADWORD: Prunelle
<hw>Pru*nelle"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., dim. of
<ets>prune</ets>. See <er>Prune</er>, <pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <def>A kind
